      "score": 335,
      "comments": 165,
      "author": "tjek",
      "published": "2026-05-26T23:36:06Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Execute feature flags at the edge using Cloudflare Workers to eliminate latency and avoid origin server roundtrips during user requests.",
        "Enable progressive delivery and A/B testing globally with Flagship's Edge SDK integrated into your Cloudflare serverless pipeline.",
        "Reduce client-side SDK footprint and improve Core Web Vitals by moving feature flagging decisions to Cloudflare's 300+ edge locations."
      ]
    },
